inking, this is essential reading for academics and students interested in social theory and theories of criminology.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aCriminologyxPhilosophy. 0aCriminology. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Criminology.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBristol University Press Complete eBook-Package 2015z978311119642840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781447327332423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781447327332/original  a978-3-11-119642-8  Bristol University Press Complete eBook-Package 2015b2015  aGBV-deGruyter-alles